  "description" : "* New original short animation produced for the 30th anniversary of the Evangelion franchise.\nEvangelion Hōsō 30 Shūnen Kinen Tokubetsu Kōgyō is a newly created short anime of approximately 13 minutes, produced for the EVANGELION:30+; 30th ANNIVERSARY OF EVANGELION event. Conceived, scripted, and supervised by Hideaki Anno and directed by Naoyuki Asano, with additional supervision by Kazuya Tsurumaki, Shinji Higuchi, and Kazuki Todoroki, the short was premiered exclusively at the event in Yokohama Arena and shown once per day on a large LED screen.\nSource: Official Evangelion.jp announcement",
